Sensor Data

Tips:

In Microsoft Excel, select the following options:
Wizard Step 1:
-Delimited
-My Data has headers
Wizard Step 2:
-Semicolon
Wizard Step 3:
-General
The sensor data might have commas instead of periods, but the data will be correct for each column. Coversion to decimal can be done in Excel or R.
